        "body": "<p>While many products offer a single hero ingredient, true skin rejuvenation requires a multi-faceted strategy. The biological process of ageing is not driven by a single cause, but by a cascade of interconnected pathways. The Aliangé approach, developed by Dr. Alison Jamieson from her 40 years of clinical practice, is designed to intervene at multiple points in this cascade.</p>",
